---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import Schema from '../../components/Schema.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../lib/site';

// Lead with definitive 1-sentence answer; ~50 words per FAQ for AI Overview citation.
const faqs = [
  { q: 'How much does an AC tune-up cost in Wesley Chapel & Tampa?', a: 'Single 21-point tune-ups run <strong>$99–$159 in 2026</strong>. The annual plan bundles two seasonal visits plus priority dispatch, 15% repair discount, and no-cost diagnostics for $189–$249/yr — it pays for itself if you need even one minor repair.' },
  { q: 'How often should I service my AC in Tampa?', a: 'Twice a year. Once before cooling season (March/April) and once before heating season (October). Tampa Bay AC systems run 2,200+ hours per year against constant humidity — about 4× the load of northern climates — so a single annual visit isn\'t enough.' },
  { q: 'What\'s included in your 21-point AC tune-up?', a: 'Coil wash, refrigerant superheat/subcool, capacitor microfarad test, contactor inspection, blower amp draw, condensate drain flush, thermostat calibration, electrical tightening, static pressure check, temperature split, and a full written report with photos.' },
  { q: 'Will AC maintenance actually lower my electric bill?', a: 'Yes — measurably. A dirty coil and low refrigerant can drop efficiency 20–30%. We routinely see Wesley Chapel homeowners save $30–$60 per month in summer after a tune-up, and catch $400+ repairs before they happen.' },
  { q: 'Does maintenance cover warranty requirements?', a: 'Yes. Most manufacturer warranties (Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Goodman, Rheem) require documented annual maintenance to stay valid. We provide a dated photographic report you can file for warranty claims.' },
  { q: 'Do you offer a maintenance plan?', a: 'Yes — two scheduled visits per year, priority dispatch during heat waves, 15% off any parts/repairs, waived after-hours fees, and a documented service history. $189–$249 per year depending on system count.' },
];

const related = [
  { href: '/services/ac-repair-tampa/', label: 'Same-day AC repair' },
  { href: '/services/air-duct-cleaning-tampa/', label: 'Air duct cleaning' },
  { href: '/services/thermostat-installation-tampa/', label: 'Smart thermostat upgrade' },
  { href: '/services/hvac-installation-tampa/', label: 'When it\'s time to replace' },
];

const areaLinks = [
  { href: '/service-areas/wesley-chapel-ac-repair/', label: 'AC tune-ups in Wesley Chapel', note: 'Foamflower Blvd HQ' },
  { href: '/service-areas/lutz-home-air-conditioning-service/', label: 'AC tune-ups in Lutz', note: 'Avila · Cheval' },
  { href: '/service-areas/odessa-emergency-ac-repair/', label: 'AC tune-ups in Odessa', note: 'Keystone · Starkey Ranch' },
];

const maintenancePrices = SITE.priceList.filter(p =>
  p.item.includes('tune-up') || p.item.includes('Annual')
);
---
<ServiceLayout
  slug="ac-maintenance-tampa"
  title="AC Maintenance & Tune-Ups in Wesley Chapel, FL | I Care Air Care"
  description="21-point AC tune-ups & maintenance plans in Wesley Chapel, New Tampa, Land O' Lakes, Lutz & Tampa. Catch problems early, lower bills, keep your warranty valid. Call (813) 395-2324."
  h1="AC Maintenance & Tune-Ups in Wesley Chapel & Tampa, FL"
  eyebrow="Preventive Maintenance · Wesley Chapel"
  subtitle={`Tampa Bay humidity, salt-air corrosion, and near-year-round runtime wear Wesley Chapel and Tampa HVAC systems faster than anywhere else in the country. A proper <span class="text-accent-400 font-semibold">preventive tune-up twice a year</span> is the single best thing you can do for comfort and energy bills.`}
  heroImage="/images/HVAC-Services-in-Tampa-FL-%E2%80%93-AC-Refrigerant-Pressure-Testing.webp"
  serviceName="AC Maintenance"
  faqs={faqs}
  related={related}
  areaLinks={areaLinks}
  priceRange="$99-$249"
>
  <h2>Why Wesley Chapel AC systems need more maintenance than most</h2>
  <p>A Minnesota AC runs maybe 600 hours a year. A Wesley Chapel or Tampa AC runs <strong>2,200+ hours a year</strong>. Combine that with constant 70–95% humidity, salt aerosol drifting inland from the Gulf, and the pollen loads of Pasco County's pine and oak canopy that clog coils twice as fast as drier climates, and you have a system working harder and dirtier than the industry average. Contractors who sell you an annual tune-up schedule built for Georgia are doing you a disservice.</p>

  <p>Our maintenance program is built specifically for Wesley Chapel, New Tampa, Land O' Lakes and greater Tampa Bay homes: <strong>two full visits per year</strong>, timed to prep for cooling season and heating season, with extra attention to the corrosion, drain-line biofilm, and coil fouling that dominate Florida HVAC failures.</p>

  <h2>Our 21-point AC tune-up — what we actually do</h2>
  <p>No vague "inspect the unit" bullet points. Here's exactly what happens when our technician pulls into your driveway:</p>
  <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700 mt-4">
    <li>Visual inspection of outdoor unit, disconnect, and refrigerant line insulation</li>
    <li>Condenser coil wash with approved non-acid coil cleaner</li>
    <li>Evaporator coil inspection (and cleaning when accessible)</li>
    <li>Refrigerant pressure check with manifold gauges — including superheat and subcool</li>
    <li>Capacitor microfarad test against nameplate spec (weak caps fail early)</li>
    <li>Contactor inspection for pitting and burn marks</li>
    <li>Condenser fan motor amp draw and shaft bearing check</li>
    <li>Blower wheel cleaning and balance check</li>
    <li>Blower motor amp draw vs. nameplate</li>
    <li>Electrical connection tightening at contactor, disconnect, and panel</li>
    <li>Thermostat calibration and program review</li>
    <li>Condensate drain line flush with wet-vac and biocide treatment</li>
    <li>Float switch / safety switch test</li>
    <li>Air filter inspection (replaced if you supply a spare)</li>
    <li>Static pressure test across the coil and filter</li>
    <li>Return and supply temperature split (should be 15–22°F)</li>
    <li>Ductwork check for leaks and insulation at accessible runs</li>
    <li>Compressor amp draw and start-up test</li>
    <li>Outdoor fan start-up and run test</li>
    <li>Full photographic report emailed to you within 24 hours</li>
    <li>Written equipment-age estimate and recommended-action timeline</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>What maintenance catches (and saves you)</h2>
  <p>Over the last 12 months our maintenance visits in Wesley Chapel and Tampa caught, on average: a 15% undercharge on refrigerant (dropping efficiency 22%); a capacitor reading 30% below spec (weeks from failure); a biofilm-clogged drain line that would have overflowed into ceiling drywall. Fixed at a maintenance visit for under $50 each. Fixed after failure? $400+, plus a night without cooling.</p>

  <h2>The I Care Air Care maintenance plan</h2>
  <p>For homeowners who want it handled: our annual plan bundles both seasonal tune-ups, priority dispatch during heat waves, 15% off any parts/repairs you ever need, waived after-hours fees, and a documented service history for manufacturer warranties. Members also get first-in-line scheduling the week after a major storm — when we're otherwise booked 5 days out.</p>

  <p>Ready to set it and forget it? <a href="/contact/">Enroll online</a> or call <a href="tel:+18133952324">(813) 395-2324</a> — we'll schedule your first visit this week.</p>

  <h2>2026 maintenance pricing — what to expect</h2>
  <div class="not-prose my-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl ring-1 ring-slate-200">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead class="bg-surface text-navy-700">
        <tr><th class="text-left py-2 px-4 font-semibold">Service</th><th class="text-left py-2 px-4 font-semibold">2026 flat-rate</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="text-slate-700">
        {maintenancePrices.map(p => (
          <tr class="border-t border-slate-100"><td class="py-2 px-4">{p.item}</td><td class="py-2 px-4 font-mono">${p.min}{p.max !== p.min ? `–$${p.max}` : ''}</td></tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <Schema
    slot="extraSchema"
    type="PriceSpecificationList"
    prices={maintenancePrices}
    pageId={`${SITE.url}/services/ac-maintenance-tampa/`}
    data={{ name: '2026 AC maintenance pricing in Wesley Chapel & Tampa Bay' }}
  />
</ServiceLayout>
